{"tid":1960082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇連仔話我知，黃金逼爆人係為左買咩GAME？","createTime":"2020-04-06T01:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:30:54.000Z","uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1211ea152a8ddb46787617c77371221d1535f8bd","tid":1960082,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:58:48.000Z","msg":"打機迷塞爆深水埗黃金商場 墟冚場面恐埋播毒危機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200405%2Fbkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=711e63ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/photo/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200405163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200405163054&h=ee624b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗黃金商場人頭湧湧。(李志湧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/photo/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_02p.jpg?20200405163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20200405163054&h=b67ce256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「禁聚令」實施下，黃金商場仍出現逼爆景象。(李志湧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/photo/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_03b.jpg?20200405163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20200405163054&h=dbbdd2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少打機發燒友無懼疫情外出選購電子遊戲。(李志湧攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200405/photo/bkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_04b.jpg?20200405163054\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200405141626723-0405_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20200405163054&h=eaa5e5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商場環境非常狹窄，墟冚場面隱藏播毒危機。<br />\n<br />\n港府上周日(3月29日)起實施「禁聚令」，限制4人以上在公眾地方聚集，亦呼籲市民居留在家中減少外出。不過，深水埗黃金商場今日(5)仍見人頭湧湧，商場逼爆，雖然大部分市民有戴上口罩，但一眾打機發燒友選購心頭好時，無懼人群聚集，商場內窄巷擠得水洩不通，出現「人貼人」，猶如行年宵的熱鬧場面，墟冚場面埋藏播毒危機。<br />\n<br />\n不知是否市民困在家中避疫逾數月，需要搜羅電子遊戲在家解悶，黃金商場一帶的市民不減反增，商場內不斷出現人潮，猶如行年宵般熱鬧，特別在一些出售電子遊戲、並設有專人講解打機攻略的店鋪外，吸引發燒友駐足觀看。但東網記者現場所見不少店舖並無提供特別防疫措施，亦見不到提供有酒精搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗一帶攤檔亦出現人群聚集，逾半屬外傭人士趁假日選購平貨，搶購電子用品、防疫產品等，假日人多擠迫的畫面重臨。"},{"pid":"5367d48b80c07821cad204060dc6bd8b698610d0","tid":1960082,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"有冇有份去既連仔話我知，咩GAME咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d54d56048b24748cbcf4ad54950f15fb3a11f4","tid":1960082,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:59:22.000Z","msg":"Switch"},{"pid":"6d9d55e52f0c363ca6933bf78bf70418248223fc","tid":1960082,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23d54d56048b24748cbcf4ad54950f15fb3a11f4","tid":1960082,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:59:22.000Z","msg":"Switch"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:59:41.000Z","msg":"唔係斷哂無貨出咩？"},{"pid":"3990f142a61154adfa92b573491e309635bb59f8","tid":1960082,"uid":180302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"On9先去黃金 全港無論game定機<br />\n都係黃金炒得最貴"},{"pid":"1eb28ebfc34f5c44a4217fba326d0fef34be0d66","tid":1960082,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3990f142a61154adfa92b573491e309635bb59f8","tid":1960082,"uid":180302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"